metadata.name: Nuri
metadata.description:
Nuri is a master of the ancient dance form Kuma, and a black belt martial artist (Emerald Tiger Clan). Her palms emit light while she dances, and her movements can harmonize others’ energy fields, creating instant release and healing. She is one of the original Keepers of the Flame delegation. 


1/1
Maniko: Keepers Of The Flame
